Abstract. VVe present in this paper a syntactico—semantics tagger prototype which uses as
first linguistic resources various dictionaries elaborated at LDI. First, we mention several
related works. Second, we present the overall sketch of the system. Third, we expose the main
characteristics of the syntactico—semantic dictionaries implied in the processes. Last, using an
example, we explicit the main stages of the analysis.

